40
00:04:46,595 --> 00:04:49,532
Oh Mr. Ages, my son Timothy is so sick!

41
00:04:49,533 --> 00:04:52,116
Timmy? The one with the spider bite?

42
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,812
Oh, just give him some pepsissiwa root and...

43
