54
00:05:15,462 --> 00:05:15,977
..yes?

55
00:05:15,977 --> 00:05:18,028
...and there's a raspy sound when he breathes.

56
00:05:18,028 --> 00:05:20,569
A raspy sound you say? Well..

57
00:05:23,548 --> 00:05:24,995
