123
00:08:24,774 --> 00:08:28,213
Look towards the house. See
if you can see him.

124
00:08:28,214 --> 00:08:32,824
Come back down here!

125
00:08:32,825 --> 00:08:34,629
He'll see you for sure up there!

126
00:08:34,630 --> 00:08:37,059
Hey, there's a cat out there!

127
00:08:37,060 --> 00:08:39,400
