146
00:09:49,001 --> 00:09:52,219
Oh...fiddlesticks. Hold still.

147
00:09:52,220 --> 00:09:55,974
If I had actually been near a cat, I'd be sneezing my brains out.

148
00:09:55,975 --> 00:09:57,639
See, I'm allergic to ca...

