I'm allergic to caaaaa...

151
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:10,917
I'm allerg...AHHH-CHOOOO!

152
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:13,336
Excuse me, pardon me.

153
00:10:50,800 --> 00:10:52,954
The string, quick! Grab the string!

154
00:11:44,794 --> 00:11:47,800
Hey, Miss Mouse, don't worry, I'm ok.

155
00:11:51,783 --> 00:11:52,800
See? I'm alright.

156
00:11:52,801 --> 00:11:54,979
That's not the reason I'm crying.

157
00:11:55,881 --> 00:11:57,757
