184
00:13:18,575 --> 00:13:21,016
Right. When you're right, you're right.

185
00:13:21,328 --> 00:13:22,523
And you're right.

186
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:25,338
None of the girls I meet want to get serious!

187
00:13:25,603 --> 00:13:27,514
