for the welfare of the entire field is monstrous!

218
00:15:14,188 --> 00:15:15,848
Brisby!

219
00:15:15,849 --> 00:15:17,080
mother isn't here

220
00:15:17,081 --> 00:15:19,875
Auntie Shrew, Timmy's sick!

221
00:15:19,876 --> 00:15:22,992
Cynthia dearest, don't pull me.

222
00:15:24,099 --> 00:15:25,622
She's not here?

223
00:15:26,131 --> 00:15:28,292
She left you children alone then?

224
00:15:28,293 --> 00:15:29,478
I'm old enough.

225
00:15:29,479 --> 00:15:32,964
...rats in the field up to heaven knows what sort of mischief...

226
00:15:32,965 --> 00:15:35,134
Cynthia dear, don't fidgit!

227
00:15:35,135 --> 00:15:36,837
You're so like your mother!

228
00:15:36,838 --> 00:15:38,397
I ain't scared of nuthin!

229
00:15:38,398 --> 00:15:40,521
She went to see Mr. Ages.

230
00:15:40,522 --> 00:15:43,429
To Ages? That old flim-flam!

231
00:15:43,430 --> 00:15:44,452
