232
00:15:44,453 --> 00:15:46,465
Auntie Shrew, Timmy's sick!

233
00:15:46,466 --> 00:15:48,353
Patience, my pet.

234
00:15:48,354 --> 00:15:50,223
Why to Ages?

235
00:15:50,224 --> 00:15:52,884
-Timmy's sick!
-Timothy is very ill.

236
00:15:52,885 --> 00:15:55,544
Timmy ill? How dreadful!

237
00:15:55,545 --> 00:15:57,458
I'm not afraid of the dark!

238
00:15:57,458 --> 00:16:00,000
I'm not afraid of the farmer!

239
00:16:00,001 --> 00:16:00,962
I can't hear!

240
00:16:00,963 --> 00:16:02,625
I'm not even scared of Dragon.

241
00:16:03,192 --> 00:16:06,486
