244
00:16:08,528 --> 00:16:09,328
Martin!

245
00:16:09,329 --> 00:16:10,612
Precocious monster!

246
00:16:10,613 --> 00:16:12,121
Bossing bullfrog!

247
00:16:12,122 --> 00:16:13,687
Spoiled brat!

248
00:16:13,688 --> 00:16:14,960
Loudmouth!

249
